---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { Brain, Heart, Users, Target, BookOpen, ArrowRight } from 'lucide-react';
---

<BaseLayout title="Mental Health Articles & Resources | RealMindSolutions" description="Comprehensive mental health resources—articles, guides, assessments, therapy platforms, and tools for improving mental well-being and finding effective treatment.">
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-b from-white via-brand-primary-50/30 to-white pt-16 pb-12 md:pt-24 md:pb-16">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12">
      <h1 class="font-heading text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-6">Mental Health Resources</h1>
      <p class="font-serif italic text-lg md:text-xl text-neutral-600">Comprehensive resources for understanding, managing, and improving your mental health.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-white py-12 md:py-16">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12">
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-12">
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
          Mental health is as important as physical health. This hub brings together all our mental health content: condition-specific resources, therapy platform reviews, self-help tools, crisis support, and evidence-based treatment information.
        </p>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">Mental Health Resources by Topic</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-12">
        <a href="/blog/tag/anxiety" class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 to-cyan-50 rounded-lg p-6 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow border border-blue-100">
          <Brain className="h-6 w-6 text-blue-600 mb-3" />
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Anxiety Resources</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mb-3">Comprehensive anxiety resources, treatment options, and coping strategies.</p>
          <div class="flex items-center text-sm text-blue-700 font-semibold">
            <ArrowRight className="h-4 w-4 mr-1" />View Anxiety Hub
          </div>
        </a>

        <a href="/blog/tag/depression" class="bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-50 to-pink-50 rounded-lg p-6 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow border border-purple-100">
          <Heart className="h-6 w-6 text-purple-600 mb-3" />
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Depression Resources</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mb-3">Support groups, therapy options, and tools for managing depression.</p>
          <div class="flex items-center text-sm text-purple-700 font-semibold">
            <ArrowRight className="h-4 w-4 mr-1" />View Depression Hub
          </div>
        </a>

        <a href="/tools/assessments" class="bg-gradient-to-br from-green-50 to-teal-50 rounded-lg p-6 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow border border-green-100">
          <Target className="h-6 w-6 text-green-600 mb-3" />
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Mental Health Assessments</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mb-3">Free screening tools for anxiety, depression, OCD, PTSD, and more.</p>
          <div class="flex items-center text-sm text-green-700 font-semibold">
            <ArrowRight className="h-4 w-4 mr-1" />Take Assessments
          </div>
        </a>

        <a href="/resources/guides/crisis-resources" class="bg-gradient-to-br from-red-50 to-orange-50 rounded-lg p-6 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow border border-red-100">
          <Users className="h-6 w-6 text-red-600 mb-3" />
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Crisis Resources</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mb-3">24/7 hotlines, crisis text lines, and emergency mental health support.</p>
          <div class="flex items-center text-sm text-red-700 font-semibold">
            <ArrowRight className="h-4 w-4 mr-1" />Get Help Now
          </div>
        </a>

        <a href="/best/conditions" class="bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-50 to-blue-50 rounded-lg p-6 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow border border-indigo-100">
          <BookOpen className="h-6 w-6 text-indigo-600 mb-3" />
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Best Platforms by Condition</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mb-3">Top therapy platforms for specific mental health conditions.</p>
          <div class="flex items-center text-sm text-indigo-700 font-semibold">
            <ArrowRight className="h-4 w-4 mr-1" />Browse by Condition
          </div>
        </a>

        <a href="/resources/worksheets" class="bg-gradient-to-br from-yellow-50 to-amber-50 rounded-lg p-6 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow border border-yellow-100">
          <BookOpen className="h-6 w-6 text-yellow-600 mb-3" />
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Mental Health Worksheets</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mb-3">Free downloadable worksheets for CBT, mindfulness, mood tracking, and more.</p>
          <div class="flex items-center text-sm text-yellow-700 font-semibold">
            <ArrowRight className="h-4 w-4 mr-1" />Browse Worksheets
          </div>
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-200 p-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Mental Health Blog Articles</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">We're building a comprehensive library of mental health articles. Future posts will cover:</p>
        <ul class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-3 text-sm text-gray-700 mb-6">
          <li>• Mental health stigma: challenging misconceptions</li>
          <li>• Self-care strategies for mental wellness</li>
          <li>• The mind-body connection in mental health</li>
          <li>• Building resilience and emotional strength</li>
          <li>• Mental health in different life stages</li>
          <li>• Cultural perspectives on mental health</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Explore our existing mental health resources above while we continue building our blog library.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-gray-50 py-12 md:py-16">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Related Topics</h2>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
        <a href="/blog/tag/anxiety" class="px-4 py-2 bg-white hover:bg-gray-100 rounded-full text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 transition-colors">Anxiety</a>
        <a href="/blog/tag/depression" class="px-4 py-2 bg-white hover:bg-gray-100 rounded-full text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 transition-colors">Depression</a>
        <a href="/blog/tag/therapy" class="px-4 py-2 bg-white hover:bg-gray-100 rounded-full text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 transition-colors">Therapy</a>
        <a href="/blog/tag/self-care" class="px-4 py-2 bg-white hover:bg-gray-100 rounded-full text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 transition-colors">Self-Care</a>
        <a href="/blog/tag/mindfulness" class="px-4 py-2 bg-white hover:bg-gray-100 rounded-full text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 transition-colors">Mindfulness</a>
        <a href="/blog/tag/relationships" class="px-4 py-2 bg-white hover:bg-gray-100 rounded-full text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 transition-colors">Relationships</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
